Revenue:
$311,105,920





                                            Miscellaneous nonmetallic minerals, except fuels company Stillwater Mining Co runs main operations out of Billings, MT. It boasts an annual revenue of $311.1 million and employs 2,488 people. Though Stillwater Mining Co has yet to hit the mainstream, it's found niche success. The firm is run by CEO Francis R Mcallister.
                                        









