Time at Stillwater Mining Co

























                                                Candidates seeking jobs at Stillwater Mining Co hail from universities all over the country, but certain institutions stand out above the rest. Laurel High School  alumni represent 7.69%, North Idaho college accounts for 7.69% of candidates, and Powell High makes up 7.69%.
                                            

                                                Trends in employee education at Stillwater Mining Co provide important insight into the company's intellectual environment. In terms of educational backgrounds at Stillwater Mining Co, the most common among employees is high school graduate (46.15% of workers).
                                            

